# Phase 4: Smart Features — Implementation Plan

## Overview

This phase adds two smart layers on top of the existing FocusTrack foundation:
1. **App Limits & Alerts** — users set a daily time cap per app; the API evaluates usage and flags breaches.
2. **Automated Weekly Email Report** — a background Hangfire job generates and sends a weekly HTML summary via MailKit/SMTP.
3. **Settings UI** — a new Angular page where users manage their app limits.

The project is .NET 10 / SQLite (dev) and Angular 17+ standalone.

---

